Package org.oucs.oxpoints.test.classes Description

Contains various unit tests to test the functionality of the OxPoints system.

Although the tests are far from being exhaustive they will give you a good indication of whether you introduced bugs by extending the system. If one of these tests (run TestAllRealModel to run all unit tests) fails you should either have a very good explanation or you should go back to your code and search for bugs.

Since many tests add or remove data they should not be run to test a live system.
